\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b0\i0 All good so far, I hope. Now let\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s familiarise ourselves with some other basic features. Click on \u8220\'93Step 4: Full Screen\u8221\'94 in the binder.}}